{"TopicId":161006,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"KIS/KAS easter egg discovered!","CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-24T19:37:42Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-24T19:37:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi guys!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\na few days ago I installed both \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E via \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E. Now, whenever I open up KSP, all the little kerbals on the loading screen carry tiny little electric drills and backpacks \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E.\u00A0Val even has a chunk of C4!!!!\u00A0I hope this is intentional, because it is very funny and cute \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPics for proof\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=http://imgur.com/a/UX8wT\u0022 style=\u0022height:452px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Stapler","CreatedById":175205,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-24T21:01:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep, that was mentioned in the latest update release notes a few weeks ago. \u00A0It can be turned on or off from the config file so it is not necessarily an Easter egg but cool non-the-less. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"helaeon","CreatedById":101767,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-25T02:22:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou may also edit the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E config file and have them wear whatever props, tools, parts, etc that you like. So you could have them floating in space with sunglasses on if you\u0027d like.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-25T08:00:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s really cool! I have always wanted to know how to edit the title screen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Overland","CreatedById":119812,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-25T09:33:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nstep one of changing KSP to KTP \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI did wonder if the C4 could be detonated and give everyone the classic post C4 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E face\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeNapalm","CreatedById":67032,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-25T16:38:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait wait wait...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have somehow missed the sunglasses in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E?!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGAAAH!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Jn-\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}